precis:
Amendment to the DISTILLERY REGULATIONS required to facilitate the
bottling of Commonwealth Caribbean rum in Canada in accordance with the
Caribbean trade agreement known as Caribcan, and to complement
corresponding changes made to the Food and Drugs Regulations.
